			<td valign="top">
				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">Patrick FR wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">Battle city does not work well, like it is using sprites from the 2 CHR banks at the same time. Pinbal swaps sprite and backgorund banks between the title screen and the game, but Battle City is like switching sprite banks during rendering. Weird behaviour, does anyone have information about this?</div><br /><br />8x16 sprites on the NES use both pattern banks simultaneously. The sprite bank select in $2000 is ignored, and instead the LSB of each sprite's character index is used as the bank number for that sprite.</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

